-- Chavez Overcame Lung Infection, Venezuela’s Villegas Says
-- B y   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 2013-01-26T22:12:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-26/chavez-overcame-lung-infection-venezuela-s-villegas-says.html
Venezuela ’s President Hugo Chavez
overcame a lung infection he contracted after a cancer-related
surgery in Cuba last month, Information Minister Ernesto
Villegas said today on state television.  Chavez is still having some breathing problems that are
being treated, Villegas said from Santiago, Chile.  To contact the reporter on this story:
